channel.title: 4 pole (24db) low pass filter object
channel.description: I would like to suggest a 4 pole(24db) resonant low pass filter, I realize you can cascade two 2 pole filters to accomplish this same thing, but i feel it would be more effective to have a specific 4 pole 24db resonant low pass filter module.
